      • timeCode

        public final long timeCode
        Code execution time (millis) for job. Measures the time taken to execute the R code for the job.

        Can be used in conjunction with timeStart and timeTotal to profile job runtime characteristics.

      • timeTotal

        public final long timeTotal
        Total time (millis) for job. Measures the time taken to prepare R workspace and directory for job, execute code for the job and then persist job artifacts as a persistent project.

        Can be used in conjunction with timeStart and timeCode to profile job runtime characteristics.
